# DaisyUI Themes

Use **only** these themes — no other DaisyUI theme names:

| Mode | Theme | When |
|------|-------|------|
| Light | `winter` | Default / light color scheme |
| Dark | `night` | `prefers-color-scheme: dark` |

Configured in [`src/routes/layout.css`](src/routes/layout.css):

```css
@plugin 'daisyui' {
	themes: winter --default, night --prefersdark;
}
```

- Do **not** set `data-theme="corporate"` or other themes on layout wrappers
- Do **not** add theme toggle buttons that switch to other theme names unless they only toggle between `winter` and `night`

